WHY WE NEED DATABASE CONNECTION

	 Java web    <------------------------------>  DB
	application           DB CONNECTION           SERVER
	
 We send the commands to DB server and get the results via an open DB connections.
 
 Database talks SQL, but Java does not know how to talk in SQL,
  it needs a translator called JDBC (Java Database Connector)
 						  
 						  <----> Oracle
 						  <----> DB2
 	Java web   ----> JDBC <----> Sybase
	application			  <----> SQL Server
 						  <----> MySQL
  					Database specific JDBC driver
  					
